                        "displayName": "John Kelly",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I'm not able to replicate the issue with a test.  The attached test case passes.  Am I missing something?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=postalservice14",
                        "name": "postalservice14",
                        "displayName": "John Kelly",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-05-27T22:10:47.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-05-27T22:10:47.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/47809",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hhatfield",
                        "name": "hhatfield",
                        "displayName": "H Hatfield",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "When I ran the provided test, both against trunk and 1.10.1, it passed.\r\n\r\nThe only way I can get the described behavior is with the following test:\r\n{code}\r\n    public function testZF9162()\r\n    {\r\n    \t$baseUrl = 'http:\/\/foobar';\r\n        $view = new Zend_View();\r\n        $view->addBasePath(dirname(__FILE__) . '\/_files');\r\n    \r\n    \tZend_Controller_Front::getInstance()->setBaseUrl('');\r\n        \r\n        $view->baseUrl('foo.html');\r\n        Zend_Controller_Front::getInstance()->setBaseUrl($baseUrl);\r\n\r\n        $this->assertEquals($baseUrl, $view->render('testBaseUrl.phtml'));\r\n    }\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nThe difference here is calling {noformat}Zend_Controller_Front::getInstance()->setBaseUrl(){noformat} twice, once w\/ the empty string and once with the actual base url AND having a call to $view->baseUrl() in between them. This causes the BaseUrl Helper to cache the base url. ",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hhatfield",
                        "name": "hhatfield",
                        "displayName": "H Hatfield",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2011-07-30T23:23:42.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2011-07-30T23:28:25.000+0000"
                }
            ]
        }
